iquid-like ground state at least down\nto 130 mK. Furthermore, zero field specific heat shows a broad maximum around\n200 mK suggesting the presence of short-range spin correlations in this\nthree-dimensional frustrated antiferromagnet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Apr 2023 18:51:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-18"}
