gnificant improvements over simple demonstrations and previous fine-tuned\nstate-of-the-art models, e.g., improving EM, BLEU-4, and EM by at least 11.91%,\n36.88%, and 37.18% on code summarization, bug fixing and program synthesis,\nrespectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Apr 2023 15:13:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-18"}
